rake-ruby3.3 (0.1.0) wikimedia; urgency=medium

   Initial version, based on rake-ruby2.7 but on ci-trixie which
   ships Ruby 3.3. Needed by translatewiki.net which requires Ruby
   matching Debian 13 and the puppet 8 gem (Ruby >= 3.1).

